works.description: Swiss watchmaker TAG Heuer is celebrating its 150th anniversary this year. TAG Heuer has given some of the most exceptional timepieces used for competitive sports, and they were the first to master luxury chronographs with a supreme precision of 1/10th, 1/100th and 1/1,000th of a second. Now, to mark the milestone of mastering speed and celebrate the 100th anniversary of “The Greatest Spectacle in Racing,”
